Poison Swamp
RECOMMENDED LEVEL: ???
The Poison Swamp is a remote location in
Telluria only reachable by sea or air.
Once a serene lake, it's now a deadly location
filled with poison and strong monsters.
Breathing in the poison air will bring you near death,
and the monsters will most likely finish you off.
However, the reaction between the poisonous water
and minerals in the ground is rumoured to have
created some sort of rare mineral, bringing
a lot of attention to it recently.
This also brought the attention of Telluria Castle
Town, which quickly made sure that no one else
would be allowed to enter the swamp, albeit
not before a few deaths occured.
